These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, romance, sports, martial-arts, spy, time-travel, drama
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: salsa, d&b, hip-hop, funk, trance, house, folk
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, biathlon, skateboarding, snowboarding, lacrosse, swimming, baseball
 1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is between the fan of d&b and the fan of salsa##2
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 6. the person watching action movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the fan of funk is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person watching spy movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
10. the person watching drama movies is the fan of hip-hop##1
11. the fan of house is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
12. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
13. the person who's sport is soccer is the fan of trance##1
14. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is baseball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | action     | time-travel | romance | martial-arts | drama  | sports  |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | funk        | d&b  | folk     | house   | hip-hop       | trance   |
| Sport         | biathlon   | baseball | snowboarding    | skateboarding  | lacrosse | swimming | soccer |

