.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, german, dutch, pakistani, brazilian, american, spanish
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, skiing, basketball, tennis, weightlifting, lacrosse, ice-hockey
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, tram, skateboard, motorbike, bike, boat
 1. the german is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is the spanish##1
 6. the turkish is the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the turkish is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person driving the boat##2
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the brazilian##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
10. the dutch is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the brazilian is on the right of the turkish##1
12. the person driving the taxi is the german##1
13. the pakistani is on the left of the turkish##1
14. the pakistani is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
15. the german is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | american | spanish      | pakistani     | turkish  | brazilian | dutch | german |
| Sport         | skiing  | rugby | lacrosse | basketball | ice-hockey | tennis   | weightlifting  |
| Transport     | tram   | bike     | boat        | skateboard  | motorbike   | quad-bike       | taxi      |

