11. the person driving the subway is the teacher##1
12. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the dancer##1
14. the person driving the airplane is the person drinking 7up##1
15. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

