 4. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 5. the chinese is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the british is the person watching comedy movies##1
10. the chinese is the person eating nectarine##1
11. the person watching family movies is the thai##1
12. the person eating mango is the brazilian##1
13. the russian is on the far right##1
14. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching crime movies##2
15. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
