 1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 2. the owner of the rat is between the fan of techno and the fan of folk##2
 3. the fan of classical is the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the fan of pop is on the left of the designer##1
 5. the fan of classical is the doctor##1
 6. the dressmaker is in the middle##1
 7. the social-worker is the fan of soul##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the fan of classical is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the lawyer is the owner of the horse##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the videographer##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the designer##1
13. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
14. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the doctor##1
15. the lawyer is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
