 2. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the rat is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the owner of the bird##2
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
13. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
14. the person who's hobby is baking is between the owner of the hamster and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
15. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking mirinda##1

